    "description": "Build a ship with permanent and temporary upgrades and a lot of loot. Fight your way through every sector to get your cargo to the end.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Build your own build!</strong> There are a lot of weapons and ways to combine the different upgrades you get for your ship in a single run.<br></li><li><strong>Fight different factions!</strong> Three different factions can be encountered in every run and every faction has a different approach in trying to get rid of you.<br></li><li><strong>Enhance your next runs!</strong> Every run earns you credits which you can use to gain access to ship and loot improvements.<br></li><li><strong>Use different ships and pilots!</strong> There are multiple ships and pilots you can combine to change the possible loot and upgrades in your run.<br></li><li><strong>Combine items to get even better items!</strong> During a run you can combine your items in different ways to either up- or sidegrade your items.<br></li><li><strong>Fight stronger enemies in increasing danger levels!</strong> Every successful run unlocks a new danger level for you to try your skills against better enemies.</li></ul>",
